She looked at Drillbit. "He's still alive? How can this be? I thought 
he was a target of all predacons. Is he a threat to us?"

DarkMouse::
She shrugged her shoulders. "How sould I know. He's the leader here. 
Ask him." she said, gesturing to Drillbit.  She knew under KitKat's 
rule, she wouldn't get killed unless she wanted to. Under the new 
leader, she had her doubts. But for KitKat's sake, she'd stick with 
them incase they needed help. But for the most part, she was one 
mouse who looked out for number one, herself.
